&lt;td style=&#34;text-align:center&#34;&gt;一般过去时&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td style=&#34;text-align:center&#34;&gt;过去完成时&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td style=&#34;text-align:center&#34;&gt;例句&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td style=&#34;text-align:center&#34;&gt;He talks as is he would never do such things in the future.&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td style=&#34;text-align:center&#34;&gt;She looks at him as if she were his mother.&lt;/td&gt;
